Instructions for running heap_sort_selection.cpp:
execute command: make
execute command: ./heap_sort_selection seed size ith

where seed is the seed to prime the random number generator
where size is the number of elements to sort
where ith is the desired ith order statistic

The output of heap_sort_selection.cpp is automatically suppressed, if you wish 
to see the unsorted and sorted arrays generated by heap_sort_select, 
uncomment lines 158 and 161 in heap_sort_selection.cpp
